This rabbit is crying.

30
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:05,760
It isn't cute at all.

31
00:02:06,039 --> 00:02:08,080
Do you know a clever rabbit
has three burrows?

32
00:02:09,319 --> 00:02:10,599
It's cold, okay?

33
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,599
The burrow for it to hide is gone,

34
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,200
so it's crying.

35
